snippet.textDisplay:
Hey James, during this break, if you haven't seen the movies, why don't you give the Hatchet series a try when you got free time. They're a bitch to find, but hey, the Internet has everything, so I'm sure it's not going to be too difficult. Just suggesting it because the kills in those films are some of the more creative ones, at least to me. They clearly have fun with it and do not hold back on the gore whatsoever, plus the series (except Victor Crowley) takes place on the EXACT SAME NIGHT the whole time, which most slashes avoid. I'm not giving any major spoilers of course, I think it is a series someone should enter blind.
Have fun on your break man, we're gonna miss the weekly stuff but we know that you deserve a break. Just make sure you don't end up.....
DEAD MEAT on us 😂
G-Get? Cause it's the chan- okay I'll stop talking now.
